{"tid":1043792,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大啟動孟晚舟引渡程序   中國：對華高科企政治迫害","createTime":"2019-03-02T13:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T14:31:23.000Z","uid":66271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98072b1b8db20850cd654355bae025b8815b781f","tid":1043792,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"華為集團副董事長孟晚舟被美國刑事起訴一案，加拿大司法部批准法院啟動引渡聆訊程序，法庭下周三排期聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n中國強烈不滿，向加拿大提出嚴正交涉，再次敦促立即放人，又批評案件是對中國高科技企業的政治迫害。<br />\n<br />\n美國就讚揚加拿大政府堅持法治。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #加拿大 #華為 #孟晚舟 #美國 #中國"},{"pid":"a2817d0dc037fa718765511b24c58d9ecbebb823","tid":1043792,"uid":15133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/214601_57539396abac1d32baaaffa2c3e1a375.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F214601_57539396abac1d32baaaffa2c3e1a375.png&h=d21e7b8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1ad31562ad7cf23fe94bfb7c412f7a8c7b308f7","tid":1043792,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"牛軍頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47758c10058e1d97810b162936446394f8f204a3","tid":1043792,"uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1ad31562ad7cf23fe94bfb7c412f7a8c7b308f7","tid":1043792,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"牛軍頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"黑期咩事都冇，已消化，劍指32000<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6583590446034afea8e3edf411bbd331df90335","tid":1043792,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:31:23.000Z","msg":"開緊全國兩會 唔會跌"}]}